{
  "stem": "39.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was really my first meeting with the meaning of the discrimination and anti-Semitist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then a few months later, they took away my father's business too, so we had some hardship, a little.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember that my parents were very worried, because they knew that Hungary is a Fascist country, so they knew if we shall become Hungary, then it will be different than it was before when it belonged to Romania.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very concerned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, the war was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember my parents listening to the radio all the time and to the British news also, what we could hear also.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were concerned what's going to happen with the world, what's going to happen with us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we didn't think of what is going to really happen, because nobody could predict that what it's going to be.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, so basically, our life was almost the same, only more problems and more hardship and more feeling the anti-Semitic things, what went on all around.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But my life, basically, was the same, still school, still movies and going to the parks and having fun, games, the kids, homework, and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Still, I continued the lessons, private lessons also, the French, German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Still I had the music lessons, private lessons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Still I had the gym lessons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So still my parents could do that for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think it was a big sacrifice, but they did it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After his business was taken away, he just had some-- it was the stock market, the little things playing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had some investments.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had some properties, apartment house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the business, that was a big area where he had the office, a big territory where it was the lumber yard, so it was leased.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
